title: Urbanization in the United Arab Emirates 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2015.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 85.67 was reached at Year 2015
The lowest Share of urban population in total population, of value 85.07 was reported at Year 2013
